This is the Debian GNU/Linux version of the smtm stock ticker program. It
provides a configurable Perl program to display one or more stock quotes from
Yahoo! Finance, and Yahoo! UK for non-North American quotes.

This package was both written and put together for Debian by Dirk
Eddelbuettel <edd@debian.org>. The sources can also be obtained from 
	http://eddelbuettel.com/dirk/code/smtm/

Smtm is released under the GNU General Public License.  On a Debian GNU/Linux
systems, the complete text of GNU General Public License can be found in the
file /usr/share/common-licenses/GPL.


